OL,3,CGovernment expected to unveil welfare
OL,4,CBill concessions after talks with
OL,5,Crebels
OL,7,FOn Thursday night, sources said a deal
OL,8,Fwas being thrashed out between rebels
OL,9,Fand the Government as it seeks to head
OL,10,Foff the prospect of the Prime
OL,11,FMinister's first Commons defeat in a
OL,12,Fcrunch vote next week.
OL,14,FThe Government's original package
OL,15,Frestricted eligibility for the
OL,16,Fpersonal independence payment (Pip),
OL,17,Fthe main disability payment in
OL,18,FEngland, and limited the sickness-
OL,19,Frelated element of universal credit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
