OL,7,FThis would protect some 370,000
OL,8,Fexisting claimants who were expected
OL,9,Fto lose out following reassessment.
OL,11,FMinisters had hoped the reforms would
OL,12,Fget more people back into work and
OL,13,Fsave up to #5 billion a year, but
OL,14,Ffresh changes such as these would
OL,15,Fleave Chancellor Rachel Reeves needing
OL,16,Fto find money elsewhere.
