OL,7,FThe Universal Credit and Personal
OL,8,FIndependence Payment Bill has its
OL,9,Fsecond reading on Tuesday, the first
OL,10,Fopportunity for MPs to support or
OL,11,Freject it.
OL,13,FIf the legislation clears its first
OL,14,Fhurdle, it will then face a few hours'
OL,15,Fexamination by all MPs the following
OL,16,Fweek ` rather than days or weeks in
OL,17,Ffront of a committee tasked with
OL,18,Flooking at the Bill.
