OL,7,FThe Government had earlier said it was
OL,8,Flistening to suggestions to improve
OL,9,Fthe legislation amid concerns about
OL,10,Fthe swift timetable of the Bill.
OL,12,FThe so-called "reasoned amendment"
OL,13,Ftabled by Treasury select committee
OL,14,Fchairwoman Dame Meg Hillier had argued
OL,15,Fthat disabled people have not been
OL,16,Fproperly consulted and further
OL,17,Fscrutiny of the changes is needed.
