OL,7,FWhile the expected concessions look
OL,8,Fset to have reassured some of those
OL,9,Fwho had been leading the rebellion,
OL,10,Fother MPs remain opposed.
OL,12,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, Rachel
OL,13,FMaskell said: "As the Government is
OL,14,Fseeking to reform the system they
OL,15,Fshould protect all disabled people
OL,16,Funtil they have completed their co-
OL,17,Fproduced consultation and co-produced
OL,18,Fimplementation.
