OL,7,FSpeaking in the Commons on Wednesday,
OL,8,FSir Keir told MPs he wanted the
OL,9,Freforms to reflect "Labour values of
OL,10,Ffairness" and that discussions about
OL,11,Fthe changes would continue over the
OL,12,Fcoming days.
OL,14,FHe insisted there was "consensus
OL,15,Facross the House on the urgent need
OL,16,Ffor reform" of the "broken" welfare
OL,17,Fsystem.
